data.description: Welcome to this luxurious gem in the highly desirable ridge community! A light-filled entry warmly welcomes you with grand staircase & vaulted ceilings. The main level offers formal living & dining spaces, roomy home office, updated kitchen w/quartz countertops & stainless steel appliance. Head upstairs to find 3 bedrooms & 2 full baths, a versatile bonus room, and a spacious laundry room. Prepare to be blown away by the updated primary bedroom & stunning 5-piece ensuite bath containing built-in surround sound speakers, multiple closets, and more. This home has is all, including a huge 3-car garage with tons of storage. Extremely charming neighborhood located conveniently to shopping centers, I-5, local schools, jobs, and more!
